# Post-change checklist (UX Studio)

After changes to **code**, **UI**, or **config**, before considering the task done:

1. `npm test` (fix failures) — includes `check:links` + `check:hygiene`.
2. `npm run build` (must stay green — Pages uses the same signal).
3. Update authoritative docs if behavior changed (`docs/product/*` or `docs/projects/<id>/`). New files: [NAMING.md](docs/product/NAMING.md). Append durable lessons to [LESSONS_LEARNED.md](docs/product/LESSONS_LEARNED.md).
4. UI-facing ships: strict FE audit **PROVEN** under `docs/projects/<id>/audits/` — tests alone are BAD; browser proof for hybrid/chrome; blast-radius + REC⊗CJM⊗AIR. After domain CSS class renames: Nazi QA **light** on chrome.
5. Chrome / playback: local MCP (`__studioRunMcpSanityCheck` / `__protoRunMcpSanityCheck`, REC⊗CJM) or lean `npm run smoke` — not full marathon in CI. Agent overlay touch + sitrep settle; strip ephemeral URL params. Selectors use `data-studio-*` / `.studio-nav-*`.
6. After push (R12): optional `gh run list` peek — **do not await** CI/Pages on routine ships; await only HARD-GREEN / release / PO prove.
7. User-visible / durable seams: `npm run notes:append -- --lane=<lane> --intent="…"`.
8. Commit when coherent (and allowed). Batch push (R12): one push per coherent ship.

